cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.RO 

This paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for disparity estimation from light field images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel end-to-end network for disparity estimation, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The network is trained using large datasets, which involves optimization techniques, and hence, it can also be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the use of light field cameras, which can be categorized under cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.RO (Robotics).
